#conclusion aria-hidden="true"
  markdown:
    Notes:

    - It would have been easiest to simply associate the tooltip using `aria-describedby` to the element. But as in some screenreaders such info is only announced when the element is focused, we relied on visually hidden text instead.
    - Only works on focusable elements (would be easy to extend to non-focusable elements, though)

